content: Grapenopoly V2 - The new Crypto MetaverseGrapenopoly is a new Crypto Metaverse and NFT Play to Earn Game for BSC, Polygon, Ethereum, and Multichain Blockchains. An awesome play to earn features: - Earn Money from Your Rental Grapenopoly Property- In-game Buy Low, Sell High- Sell NFT Properties Directly- Updated 3D metaverse experiences- Open for community minting- Expand the passive income in a built-in attribute- Multi tokenization - digital and physical assets- NFTs merge - the rarity of power- Auction, marketplace, and APIs for secondary market integrationWebsite: https://grapenopoly.com/
